title: Fredrika_Stahl_-_Tributaries-2008.zip
description:
...

On her second album the swedish natural mixes Bigband sound, Swing, Jazz and Pop very well and is supported bei her 5-head-band...

...2006 debut album \\\"A Fraction Of You\\\". This album... quickly reached the top of the French jazz charts and hit top position of the Virgin jazz charts, overtaking even Norah Jones.... She now published her promising second album \\\"Tributaries\\\".

....

Just one song is an adaption of another artist. This is none less than Mike Stoller, who already composed the hits \\\"Jailhouse Rock\\\" or \\\"Hound Dog\\\" for Elvis Presley. Stoller offered the 23-year-old the so far unreleased song \\\"Monumental Mismatch\\\" written by him, which in its classic bigband arrangement reminds of Doris Day.\\\"


released 10/6/2008

enjoy!!!
